headline: Coterra Energy to Participate at Upcoming Goldman Sachs Conference
summary: HOUSTON, January 05, 2026--Coterra Energy Inc. (NYSE: CTRA) ("Coterra" or the "Company") today announced that Shane Young, Executive Vice President & Chief Financial Officer, will participate in a panel discussion at the Goldman Sachs Energy, CleanTech & Utilities Conference. The panel discussion will begin at 3:00 PM ET on Tuesday, January 6, 2026.

headline: Venezuela Fuels Broad Sector Rally But These Oil And Gas Plays Slide
summary: Venezuela news hit the stock market Monday, boosting many oil stocks, but several slid as natural gas prices sank.

headline: Why Natural Gas Prices Are Slipping Despite Strong LNG Demand
